# ML Models Cache Directory

This directory stores downloaded machine learning models to avoid re-downloading.

Models are excluded from git via .gitignore but this directory structure is preserved.

Directory structure:
- sentence-transformers/  # Observer embedding models
- whisper/                # Listener transcription models
- ollama/                 # LLM models
- spacy/                  # NLP models
- torch/                  # PyTorch cache
